1Ô∏è‚É£1Ô∏è‚É£ How FPGA is Programmed

Unlike CPUs, you don‚Äôt load software.

You configure hardware logic.

‚∏ª

Programming Flow

Write HDL code (Verilog/VHDL)
        ‚Üì
Synthesize design
        ‚Üì
Place & route
        ‚Üì
Generate bitstream
        ‚Üì
Flash into FPGA


‚∏ª

1Ô∏è‚É£2Ô∏è‚É£ HDL Languages

