‚∏ª

1Ô∏è‚É£3Ô∏è‚É£ Bitstream

Final FPGA configuration file.

Equivalent to firmware.

Contains:
	‚Ä¢	Logic layout
	‚Ä¢	Routing config
	‚Ä¢	Clock config

