‚∏ª

1Ô∏è‚É£4Ô∏è‚É£ FPGA Boot Sources

Bitstream stored in:
	‚Ä¢	SPI flash
	‚Ä¢	NOR flash
	‚Ä¢	BMC-controlled flash

