1Ô∏è‚É£7Ô∏è‚É£ FPGA vs ASIC

Feature	FPGA	ASIC
Programmable	Yes	No
Performance	Lower	Highest
Cost per unit	Higher	Lower at scale
Time to market	Fast	Slow

ASIC used in production, FPGA in design/testing.

